/// Firestore Database Schema\n/// Collections and document structures for Mystic HUB\n\n/*\n\nFIRESTORE COLLECTIONS SCHEMA:\n\n1. users/\n   - uid (document ID)\n   - email: String\n   - username: String\n   - avatar: String (URL)\n   - level: int\n   - totalPoints: int\n   - xp: int\n   - rank: int\n   - createdAt: Timestamp\n   - updatedAt: Timestamp\n   - referralCode: String\n   - referrals: int\n   - achievements: List<String>\n   - isBanned: bool\n   - isAdmin: bool\n\n2. lessons/\n   - id (document ID)\n   - title: String\n   - description: String\n   - category: String (Cardano, Web3, Gaming, etc.)\n   - icon: String (emoji)\n   - content: String\n   - order: int\n   - createdAt: Timestamp\n   - createdBy: String (admin uid)\n   - views: int\n   - difficulty: String (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced)\n\n3. memes/\n   - id (document ID)\n   - title: String\n   - imageUrl: String\n   - uploadedBy: String (user uid)\n   - likes: int\n   - uploads: List<String> (user uids who liked)\n   - createdAt: Timestamp\n   - approved: bool\n   - trending: bool\n\n4. achievements/\n   - id (document ID)\n   - title: String\n   - description: String\n   - icon: String (emoji)\n   - condition: String (description of how to unlock)\n   - rarity: String (Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary)\n   - reward: int (points)\n\n5. dailyQuests/\n   - id (document ID)\n   - title: String\n   - description: String\n   - icon: String (emoji)\n   - objective: String\n   - reward: int\n   - createdAt: Timestamp\n   - expiresAt: Timestamp\n   - difficulty: String\n   - isActive: bool\n\n6. userProgress/\n   - uid_lessonId (document ID)\n   - userId: String\n   - lessonId: String\n   - completed: bool\n   - completedAt: Timestamp\n   - timeSpent: int (seconds)\n   - score: int\n\n7. userQuests/\n   - uid_questId (document ID)\n   - userId: String\n   - questId: String\n   - completed: bool\n   - completedAt: Timestamp\n   - progress: int\n\n8. leaderboard/\n   - global (document ID)\n   - data: List<{\n       userId: String,\n       username: String,\n       points: int,\n       rank: int,\n       lastUpdated: Timestamp\n     }>\n   - lastUpdated: Timestamp\n\n9. announcements/\n   - id (document ID)\n   - title: String\n   - content: String\n   - author: String (admin uid)\n   - createdAt: Timestamp\n   - priority: String (Normal, High, Critical)\n   - isActive: bool\n\n10. gameStats/\n    - uid (document ID)\n    - userId: String\n    - gamesPlayed: int\n    - gamesWon: int\n    - totalPointsEarned: int\n    - maxCombo: int\n    - lastPlayedAt: Timestamp\n    - totalTimePlayed: int (seconds)\n\nFIREBASE STORAGE STRUCTURE:\n\n- /memes/\n  - {memeId}/image.png\n\n- /avatars/\n  - {userId}/avatar.png\n\n- /lessons/\n  - {lessonId}/\n    - thumbnail.png\n    - content.pdf (optional)\n\nSECURITY RULES (Firestore):\n\n- Only authenticated users can read/write their own documents\n- Admins can read/write all documents\n- Public leaderboard is readable by all\n- Achievements and lessons are readable by all\n- Memes require approval before visibility\n\n*/\n